casebody.data:
Arthur Brennan MALLOY, petitioner,
v.
Kenneth N. PETERS, et al. No. 15-8914. Supreme Court of the United States June 13, 2016.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
